# Patient-Caregiver Support Platform 💬❤️

An AI-powered web platform designed to support patients and their caregivers.  
The system provides secure patient–caregiver linking, mood tracking, journaling, and an integrated chatbot for emotional and informational support.

---

## 🚀 Features

- **User Authentication** (JWT-based login/signup for patients & caregivers)
- **Patient–Caregiver Linking** (patients invite caregivers by email, caregivers get linked automatically)
- **Mood Tracking** (patients submit daily surveys for mood, sleep, energy, appetite, etc.)
- **AI Chatbot** (TinyLLaMA via GPT4All for supportive conversations)
- **Frontend (React)** with role-based navigation (footer/navbar updates based on login state)
- **Backend (Node.js + Express)** with clean routes + controllers
- **Database** (MongoDB + Mongoose ORM)

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **Frontend:** React, React Router
- **Backend:** Node.js, Express
- **Database:** MongoDB
- **AI Model:** GPT4All / TinyLLaMA (local integration via Docker)
- **Authentication:** JWT

